Traveler Integrated

Home About Teaching Research Service Lab Website

Traveler Integrated is an integrated visualization system for connecting OTF2 stack traces and aggregate expression trees. It combines complex visualizations, like Atria and Ravel, while providing lower-level context, like linking to the source code performance metrics.

I contributed the code for Atria, a tree visualization. The full Traveler Integrated tool relies on several tools and the work of several other collaborators.
